    <briefdescription>
<para>Device configuration node. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Configuration node is used to manage device configurations, at least one configuration is required. It does not have an index, instead bConfigurationValue of the descriptor is used for identification. </para>
